name: Sam Bankman-Fried
summary: Former rap mogul Sean "Diddy" Combs and disgraced cryptocurrency entrepreneur Sam Bankman-Fried are reportedly being housed in the same area of a Brooklyn jail. Bankman-Fried, the founder of the now-bankrupt FTX, is awaiting trial on fraud charges after being extradited from the Bahamas. Meanwhile, Combs is behind bars after being arrested for allegedly driving while intoxicated. Also, Caroline Ellison, Bankman-Fried's former girlfriend and a former executive at FTX, was recently sentenced to two years in prison for her role in the fraud scheme that led to the company's collapse.

name: Ghost of Yotei
summary: Sony Interactive Entertainment and Sucker Punch Productions have unveiled Ghost of Yotei, the sequel to the acclaimed Ghost of Tsushima. Ghost of Yotei, set 300 years after the original, will follow a new protagonist and a story set in a new location. The game is slated for release on the PlayStation 5, taking advantage of the console's advanced capabilities, and is scheduled to launch in 2025. Ghost of Yotei, a standalone entry, expands the Ghost of Tsushima franchise, offering a fresh experience while continuing the legacy of the beloved original.
